data.description: Rare find in Walker Farms! Need space? Welcome to this 5 bedroom, 4 full bath with loft AND full finished basement. Main level primary bedroom with large ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet. In the loft, you will find a flex area with full bath. Head to the basement where you will find a complete guest suite (bedroom) full bath, walk-in closet, kitchenette and living room space!!! Basement also offers a workshop with plenty of storage. Enjoy the backyard with deck and privacy fence. No neighbors directly behind this home.
